window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>High King Brucarius 'Goldblade' Blackthorn has arrived in Timbermere.</p> <p>While Valdis Wolfbane left his past behind him along with his sword and armor, the king asks a favor of the former warrior.</p> <p>What the king does not realize is that this warrior is now a farmer. His supernatural gifts are used to toil the land and harvest crops rather than split skulls and sever limbs. Where before he commanded a squad of battle-hardened men, he now finds himself leading... an ensemble of women who love the farm just as much as he does.</p>"; 
